    {
      "id": 1,
      "authorId": 2,
      "text": "Just wrapped up an amazing product launch! 🚀 It's incredible what a dedicated team can achieve when we align on vision and execution. Looking back at the last 6 months, we've built something truly special. What launch strategies have worked best for your teams?",
      "image": "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1552664730-d307ca884978?w=800",
      "createdAt": "2026-04-20T10:00:00Z",
      "likes": 87,
      "comments": [
        {
          "id": 1,
          "authorId": 1,
          "text": "Congratulations Sarah! The product looks amazing!",
          "createdAt": "2026-04-20T11:30:00Z",
          "likes": 5
        },
        {
          "id": 2,
          "authorId": 3,
          "text": "Well done! Would love to hear more about the technical challenges.",
          "createdAt": "2026-04-20T12:15:00Z",
          "likes": 3
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "authorId": 1,
      "text": "Reflecting on the power of mentorship today. Having someone who believes in you can change everything. 💡 To all the mentors who've guided me - thank you. And to those earlier in their journey: don't be afraid to reach out. People are more willing to help than you think.",
      "image": null,
      "createdAt": "2026-04-19T14:30:00Z",
      "likes": 156,
      "comments": [
        {
          "id": 3,
          "authorId": 6,
          "text": "This is so true! Mentorship transformed my career.",
          "createdAt": "2026-04-19T15:45:00Z",
          "likes": 12
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "authorId": 5,
      "text": "Remote work has taught me that discipline > motivation. 🎯 Some days you don't feel like it, but showing up consistently is what separates good from great. What's your secret to staying productive?",
      "image": null,
      "createdAt": "2026-04-18T09:00:00Z",
      "likes": 234,
      "comments": []
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "authorId": 4,
      "text": "Designers, let's talk about accessibility. It's not a feature, it's a requirement. Here's a thread on simple ways to make your designs more inclusive 🧵",
      "image": "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1586717791821-3f44a563fa4c?w=800",
      "createdAt": "2026-04-17T16:00:00Z",
      "likes": 412,
      "comments": [
        {
          "id": 4,
          "authorId": 10,
          "text": "Thank you for sharing this! Accessibility is so important.",
          "createdAt": "2026-04-17T17:20:00Z",
          "likes": 8
        },
        {
          "id": 5,
          "authorId": 8,
          "text": "Great points! Do you have any specific tools you recommend?",
          "createdAt": "2026-04-17T18:00:00Z",
          "likes": 5
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "authorId": 6,
      "text": "Hot take: Your network is your net worth isn't just a cliché - it's reality. 🤝 I've seen more doors open through genuine relationships than perfect resumes. Start conversations, offer value, stay curious.",
      "image": null,
      "createdAt": "2026-04-16T11:30:00Z",
      "likes": 189,
      "comments": []
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
      "authorId": 9,
      "text": "Raised $2M in seed funding today! 🎉 Excited to build the future of AI with an incredible team. This is just the beginning.",
      "image": null,
      "createdAt": "2026-04-15T13:00:00Z",
      "likes": 567,
      "comments": [
        {
          "id": 6,
          "authorId": 2,
          "text": "Huge congrats Tom! Rooting for you.",
          "createdAt": "2026-04-15T13:30:00Z",
          "likes": 15
        },
        {
          "id": 7,
