          "text": "Amazing news! Looking forward to seeing what you build.",
          "createdAt": "2026-04-15T14:00:00Z",
          "likes": 10
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 7,
      "authorId": 7,
      "text": "Kubernetes tip of the day: Use resource limits wisely. Setting them too low causes OOMKills, too high wastes resources. Here's a simple formula that works for most workloads 👇",
      "image": "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1667372393119-c81c0cda748b?w=800",
      "createdAt": "2026-04-14T10:15:00Z",
      "likes": 278,
      "comments": [
        {
          "id": 8,
          "authorId": 3,
          "text": "Super helpful! Thanks for sharing.",
          "createdAt": "2026-04-14T11:00:00Z",
          "likes": 6
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 8,
      "authorId": 8,
      "text": "Just published a blog post on optimizing React performance. Covers memoization, code splitting, and lazy loading with real-world examples. Check it out!",
      "image": null,
      "createdAt": "2026-04-13T16:45:00Z",
      "likes": 145,
      "comments": []
    },
    {
      "id": 9,
      "authorId": 3,
      "text": "After 5 years of coding, here's what I wish I knew earlier: 1) Code readability > cleverness 2) Documentation is part of the feature 3) Take breaks to avoid burnout 4) Soft skills matter as much as technical ones 5) Imposter syndrome is normal, don't let it stop you",
      "image": null,
      "createdAt": "2026-04-12T09:30:00Z",
      "likes": 892,
      "comments": [
        {
          "id": 9,
          "authorId": 1,
          "text": "Absolutely! Especially #5. We all feel it.",
          "createdAt": "2026-04-12T10:15:00Z",
          "likes": 23
        },
        {
          "id": 10,
          "authorId": 5,
          "text": "Couldn't agree more. Sharing this with my team.",
          "createdAt": "2026-04-12T11:00:00Z",
          "likes": 18
        },
        {
          "id": 11,
          "authorId": 7,
          "text": "Print this and frame it. Solid advice!",
          "createdAt": "2026-04-12T12:30:00Z",
          "likes": 12
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 10,
      "authorId": 10,
      "text": "Design systems are like gardens - they need constant tending. 🌱 Spent the last quarter refining our component library and the ROI has been incredible. Faster prototyping, better consistency, happier developers.",
      "image": "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1558655146-9f40138edfeb?w=800",
      "createdAt": "2026-04-11T14:20:00Z",
      "likes": 234,
      "comments": [
        {
          "id": 12,
          "authorId": 4,
          "text": "Love the garden metaphor! So true.",
          "createdAt": "2026-04-11T15:00:00Z",
          "likes": 7
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 11,
      "authorId": 2,
      "text": "Product management is 80% communication, 15% analysis, and 5% firefighting. 📊 The best PMs I know are exceptional at bringing people together and creating clarity from chaos.",
      "image": null,
      "createdAt": "2026-04-10T11:00:00Z",
      "likes": 456,
      "comments": []
    },
    {
      "id": 12,
      "authorId": 4,
      "text": "Color contrast isn't just for WCAG compliance - it's about respecting all users. Here's a quick guide to accessible color palettes that still look amazing 🎨",
      "image": "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1541701494587-cb58502866ab?w=800",
      "createdAt": "2026-04-09T15:30:00Z",
      "likes": 312,
      "comments": [
        {
          "id": 13,
          "authorId": 10,
          "text": "Bookmarked! Thanks for this.",
          "createdAt": "2026-04-09T16:15:00Z",
          "likes": 9
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 13,
      "authorId": 1,
      "text": "Finally refactored our legacy codebase to use React hooks. Bundle size down 40%, performance up 30%, developer happiness up 1000%. 🚀 Modern patterns FTW!",
      "image": null,
      "createdAt": "2026-04-08T10:00:00Z",
      "likes": 189,
      "comments": [
        {
          "id": 14,
          "authorId": 7,
          "text": "Nice! What was the biggest challenge during migration?",
          "createdAt": "2026-04-08T11:30:00Z",
