      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 14,
      "authorId": 5,
      "text": "Machine learning isn't magic - it's math. 📐 But when applied thoughtfully, it can solve real problems and create meaningful value. Excited about the future of AI in healthcare.",
      "image": null,
      "createdAt": "2026-04-07T13:45:00Z",
      "likes": 278,
      "comments": []
    },
    {
      "id": 15,
      "authorId": 6,
      "text": "Leading a team through uncertainty requires transparency, empathy, and a steady hand. These past few months have been challenging, but I'm proud of how we've grown together. 💪",
      "image": null,
      "createdAt": "2026-04-06T16:00:00Z",
      "likes": 423,
      "comments": [
        {
          "id": 15,
          "authorId": 2,
          "text": "Your team is lucky to have you as a leader.",
          "createdAt": "2026-04-06T17:30:00Z",
          "likes": 14
        },
        {
          "id": 16,
