  "messages": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "conversationId": 1,
      "senderId": 2,
      "text": "Hey Alex! Thanks for connecting. I've been following your work on React patterns.",
      "createdAt": "2026-04-20T10:00:00Z",
      "read": true
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "conversationId": 1,
      "senderId": 1,
      "text": "Hi Sarah! Thanks for reaching out. Your PM insights have been super helpful.",
      "createdAt": "2026-04-20T10:15:00Z",
      "read": true
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "conversationId": 1,
      "senderId": 2,
      "text": "Would love to grab coffee sometime and chat about engineering productivity.",
      "createdAt": "2026-04-20T11:00:00Z",
      "read": true
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "conversationId": 1,
      "senderId": 1,
      "text": "Absolutely! How about next Tuesday?",
      "createdAt": "2026-04-20T13:00:00Z",
      "read": true
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "conversationId": 1,
      "senderId": 2,
      "text": "Tuesday works for me. Let's meet at Blue Bottle on Market St?",
      "createdAt": "2026-04-20T14:30:00Z",
      "read": false
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
      "conversationId": 2,
      "senderId": 3,
      "text": "Saw your post on mentorship. Really resonated with me!",
      "createdAt": "2026-04-19T10:00:00Z",
      "read": true
    },
    {
      "id": 7,
      "conversationId": 2,
      "senderId": 1,
      "text": "Glad you found it helpful! Happy to be a sounding board if you need one.",
      "createdAt": "2026-04-19T10:30:00Z",
      "read": true
    },
    {
      "id": 8,
      "conversationId": 2,
      "senderId": 3,
      "text": "I might take you up on that! Working on some career decisions.",
      "createdAt": "2026-04-19T11:15:00Z",
      "read": true
    },
    {
      "id": 9,
      "conversationId": 3,
      "senderId": 4,
      "text": "Love your accessibility thread! Could we collaborate on a design systems article?",
      "createdAt": "2026-04-18T15:00:00Z",
      "read": true
    },
    {
      "id": 10,
      "conversationId": 3,
      "senderId": 1,
      "text": "That would be amazing! Let's sync up next week.",
      "createdAt": "2026-04-18T15:30:00Z",
      "read": true
    },
    {
      "id": 11,
      "conversationId": 3,
      "senderId": 4,
      "text": "Perfect. I'll send over some ideas by Friday.",
      "createdAt": "2026-04-18T16:00:00Z",
      "read": true
    },
    {
      "id": 12,
      "conversationId": 3,
      "senderId": 4,
      "text": "Also, I shared your accessibility checklist with my team. Huge hit!",
      "createdAt": "2026-04-18T16:45:00Z",
      "read": false
    },
    {
      "id": 13,
      "conversationId": 4,
      "senderId": 5,
      "text": "Team, let's discuss the Q2 roadmap in our next sync.",
      "createdAt": "2026-04-17T09:00:00Z",
      "read": true
    },
    {
      "id": 14,
      "conversationId": 4,
      "senderId": 1,
      "text": "Sounds good! I'll prepare the technical spec.",
      "createdAt": "2026-04-17T09:15:00Z",
      "read": true
    },
    {
      "id": 15,
      "conversationId": 4,
      "senderId": 6,
      "text": "I'll review the user research findings before the meeting.",
      "createdAt": "2026-04-17T09:30:00Z",
      "read": true
    },
    {
      "id": 16,
      "conversationId": 4,
      "senderId": 5,
      "text": "Great coordination everyone! Looking forward to the sync.",
      "createdAt": "2026-04-17T09:20:00Z",
      "read": false
    },
    {
      "id": 17,
      "conversationId": 5,
      "senderId": 7,
      "text": "Thanks for the Kubernetes resource limits tip! Saved me hours.",
      "createdAt": "2026-04-16T12:00:00Z",
      "read": true
    },
    {
      "id": 18,
      "conversationId": 5,
      "senderId": 1,
      "text": "Happy to help! Let me know if you run into any edge cases.",
      "createdAt": "2026-04-16T12:30:00Z",
      "read": true
    },
    {
      "id": 19,
      "conversationId": 5,
      "senderId": 7,
      "text": "Will do. Coffee next week?",
      "createdAt": "2026-04-16T12:45:00Z",
      "read": true
    },
    {
      "id": 20,
      "conversationId": 5,
      "senderId": 1,
      "text": "Definitely!",
      "createdAt": "2026-04-16T13:00:00Z",
      "read": true
    },
    {
      "id": 21,
      "conversationId": 6,
      "senderId": 8,
      "text": "Hey! Heard you're working on React performance. Want to compare notes?",
      "createdAt": "2026-04-15T09:30:00Z",
      "read": true
    },
    {
      "id": 22,
      "conversationId": 6,
      "senderId": 1,
      "text": "Would love to! What areas are you focusing on?",
      "createdAt": "2026-04-15T10:00:00Z",
      "read": true
    },
    {
      "id": 23,
      "conversationId": 6,
      "senderId": 8,
      "text": "Mainly bundle optimization and code splitting. Getting some good results.",
      "createdAt": "2026-04-15T10:15:00Z",
      "read": true
    },
    {
      "id": 24,
      "conversationId": 6,
      "senderId": 8,
      "text": "Reduced our initial bundle by 60% using dynamic imports!",
      "createdAt": "2026-04-15T10:30:00Z",
      "read": false
    },
    {
      "id": 25,
      "conversationId": 7,
      "senderId": 9,
      "text": "Alex! Congrats on the product launch. Would love to hear about the technical challenges.",
      "createdAt": "2026-04-14T14:00:00Z",
      "read": true
    },
    {
      "id": 26,
      "conversationId": 7,
      "senderId": 1,
      "text": "Thanks Tom! The scaling part was interesting - happy to share details.",
      "createdAt": "2026-04-14T15:00:00Z",
      "read": true
    },
    {
      "id": 27,
      "conversationId": 7,
      "senderId": 9,
      "text": "Perfect. Podcast episode idea? 😄",
      "createdAt": "2026-04-14T15:45:00Z",
      "read": true
    },
    {
      "id": 28,
      "conversationId": 8,
      "senderId": 10,
      "text": "Love your design system work! Could I get your thoughts on our component library?",
      "createdAt": "2026-04-13T09:00:00Z",
      "read": true
    },
    {
      "id": 29,
      "conversationId": 8,
      "senderId": 1,
      "text": "Absolutely! Send me the Figma link and I'll take a look this weekend.",
      "createdAt": "2026-04-13T10:00:00Z",
      "read": true
    },
    {
      "id": 30,
      "conversationId": 8,
      "senderId": 10,
      "text": "You're the best! Here it is: [link]. Really appreciate your time!",
      "createdAt": "2026-04-13T11:00:00Z",
      "read": false
    }
